message: While some risk factors make young people more vulnerable to trafficking, there is no single profile of a trafficking victim and no community is immune

data.description: Human trafficking is a modern form of the oldest and most barbaric type of exploitation. It has no place in our world. San Diego businesses and community members much work together to end this atrocious crime.
data.title: Opinion: Ending Human Trafficking Is a San Diego Community Responsibility - Times of San Diego
